                    <h1 class="domdom">21</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/850">Av Festival 12: Lung Neaw Visits His Neighbours + Discussion (2011, Thailand)</a></h1>

                    <h2>21 Mar 2012, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>This debut feature by visual artist Tiravanija is a portrait of the slow passage of time and simplicity of everyday life in a small village near Chiang Mai. The artist follows old uncle Lung Neaw with a 16mm camera during his daily routines. With compassion and humility, we see him walk, talk, eat, pray, cook, hunt, smoke, drink and visit his neighbours. </p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/850">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

